Edit /etc/hosts for permanent hostname change.

Also edit, /etc/hostname.

Or use,

	#!/bin/sh

	# Log as root
	# 	su

	# Set hostname
		HNAME="New"
	
	# Store old hostname
		$PH=$(hostname)

	# Change hostname (hostnamectl) (perm)
		echo "\033[92mPermanently changed $PH to $HNAME\033[0m"
		hostnamectl set-hostname $HNAME
